X
X#HReceived: $?sfrom $s $.by $j; $b
XHReceived: $?sfrom $s $.by $j$?r with $r$.
X	($v/$V) id $i; $b
XH?P?Return-Path: <$g>
XH?D?Date: $a
XH?F?From: $q
XH?x?Full-Name: $x
XH?M?Message-ID: <$t.$i@$j>
